  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2296852">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2296852/" class="title-link">品牌的背后――《NO LOGO》读后感</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2296852"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ThinkingCat/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1012144-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ThinkingCat/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">思考的猫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-09-03"
      class="main-meta">2009-09-03 17:12:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2296852_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        对于胸怀理想主义的社会活动积极分子，我们常常怀着矛盾的心情，比如说，一帮学生深入广东某镇一知名跨国企业外包工厂，揭露其克扣工资、体罚、工作环境不达标、超时工作等行为，表述的血泪斑斑，激起社会对血汗工厂的猛烈控诉。这个时候，我们可能对他们心怀敬意，工人...

